{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922010/extras/B1nner.gif?t=1733503665\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Supports cross-play with Quest and PSVR2 player base.</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Breachers\u2122, you plan your assault or orchestrate your defense as a team through intense close-quarters combat. Whether you play as an enforcer or a revolter, master your nifty gadgetry, customize your powerful weaponry and beat your opponents in stunning environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922010/extras/B2nner.gif?t=1733503665\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BREACH AS ENFORCER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal as an enforcer is to eliminate your enemies and disarm their bombs with an EMP. Rappel and blow up walls, swing through windows and catch your opponents by surprise with gadgetry like drones, cloaking devices, flashbangs and breaching foam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922010/extras/B3nner.gif?t=1733503665\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AMBUSH AS REVOLTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal as a revolter is to prevent your enemies from disarming your bomb by terminating them before they do so. Use doorblockers, tripmines, static field emitters and proximity sensors to defend your position.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922010/extras/B4nner.gif?t=1733503665\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CUSTOMIZE POWERFUL WEAPONRY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To ensure victory, purchase and customize your extensive weaponry to your liking at the start of each round. Every gun, whether it's pistols, SMGs, shotguns or assault rifles, can be modified with attachments to suit your needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922010/extras/B5nner.gif?t=1733503665\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLAY ON A VARIETY OF MAPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the rooftop of a modern city skyscraper, to taking back a research facility in the Arctic. A great variety of maps await your arrival, and frequent content updates will keep you engaged and playing!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"On Point","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/4bbc7f299e32658d90652fb1192686a0663c7570.jpg"},{"name":"Neurosurgeon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/7aefc11680e5312fb05043b2f8851def50eb0c57.jpg"},{"name":"Cheap skills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/236a9f08e047b75ca9633e961f78d45a81a79193.jpg"},{"name":"Can\u2019t Touch This","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/4aafd880e22bd897ba155360439910784ed39258.jpg"},{"name":"MVP","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/b2fbde75055c3f56142d8bf2d1173d9f1f2459e3.jpg"},{"name":"Well Aimed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/32814056dddfba1e88c2ce32f4a54764203a81aa.jpg"},{"name":"Well Trained","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/1b94642bfc0a4794607a6c5539f103f4553786b1.jpg"},{"name":"Revolt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/844a248e0eb7bfde1ca8fecf1e63badc62ac60cc.jpg"},{"name":"Enforce","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1922010/39fe4f85